headline: Xcel Energy Announces Cash Tender Offers for up to $110,000,000 of Outstanding First Mortgage Bonds Issued By Northern States Power Company (a Minnesota corporation)
summary: Xcel Energy Inc. (NASDAQ: XEL) (Xcel Energy) announced today the commencement of offers to purchase for cash (the Tender Offers) up to $110,000,000 aggregate principal amount (the Aggregate Tender Cap) of the outstanding first mortgage bonds issued by Northern States Power Company, a Minnesota corporation (NSPM), a wholly owned subsidiary of Xcel Energy, listed in the table below (the Bonds).
